      <P align=center class=MsoNormal style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%">　</P>
      <P align=center class=MsoNormal style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%"><strong><font color="#ff0000"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 26pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">电磁兼容(EMC)设计与测试技术研修班</span></font></strong></P>
      <P align=center class=MsoNormal style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%"><STRONG><SPAN 
      style="FONT-FAMILY: 华文中宋; FONT-SIZE: 13pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT 
